<p><b>Edith Wharton</b> (January 24, 1862 – August 11, 1937) was an <a href="/wiki/United_States" title="United States">American</a> <a href="/wiki/Novelist" title="Novelist" class="mw-redirect">novelist</a>, <a href="/wiki/Short_story" title="Short story">short story</a> <a href="/wiki/Writer" title="Writer">writer</a> and <a href="/wiki/Design" title="Design">designer</a>.<sup id="cite_ref-obit_0-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-obit-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
<table id="toc" class="toc" summary="Contents">
