<li id="cite_note-8"><b><a href="#cite_ref-8" title="">^</a></b> Entry for Edith Wharton written by Judith E. Funston in <i>American National Biography</i>, New York, Oxford University Press, 1999, Vol 23, pp. 111–112. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0195128028" class="internal">ISBN 0-19-512802-8</a>.</li>
<li id="cite_note-9"><b><a href="#cite_ref-9" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.patrimoine-de-france.org/oeuvres/richesses-50-14636-105627-M157434-258679.html" class="external text" title="http://www.patrimoine-de-france.org/oeuvres/richesses-50-14636-105627-M157434-258679.html" rel="nofollow">Domaine du Pavillon Colombe à Saint-Brice-sous-Forêt (95)</a></li>
</ol>
</div>
<p><a name="External_links" id="External_links"></a></p>
